@startuml Weight Tracking Flow
!theme vibrant
title LilyFit - Weight Tracking Flow

actor User
participant "ProgressScreen" as Progress
participant "WeightChartCard" as Chart
participant "WeightEntryDialog" as Dialog
participant "AppProvider" as Provider
participant "SupabaseService" as Supabase
participant "UserProfile" as Profile

== View Weight Progress ==

User -> Progress: Navigate to Progress tab
activate Progress

Progress -> Provider: Get weight data
activate Provider
Provider --> Progress: weightEntries list,\ncurrent weight,\nBMI, BMI category
deactivate Provider

Progress -> Chart: Render weight chart
activate Chart

Chart -> Chart: Calculate statistics:\n- Current weight\n- Starting weight\n- Total change\n- Trend (gaining/losing)\n- Average weekly change

Chart --> User: Display line chart:\n- X-axis: Dates\n- Y-axis: Weight (kg/lbs)\n- Show data points\n- Trend line\n- Current BMI: 23.5 (Normal)

deactivate Chart

== Add Weight Entry ==

User -> Progress: Click "Add Weight" / "+" button

Progress -> Dialog: Show weight entry dialog
activate Dialog

Dialog -> Provider: Get current weight & unit
activate Provider
Provider --> Dialog: weight: 75 kg, unit: "kg"
deactivate Provider

Dialog --> User: Show dialog:\n- Current: 75.0 kg\n- Slider/Input to adjust\n- Unit toggle (kg/lbs)\n- Date picker (default: today)

User -> Dialog: Adjust weight to 74.5 kg
User -> Dialog: Select date (if not today)
User -> Dialog: Click "Save"

Dialog -> Provider: addWeight(74.5)
activate Provider

Provider -> Provider: Get today's date
Provider -> Provider: Remove today's entry\n(if exists - replace)
Provider -> Provider: Add new WeightEntry:\n  - date: today\n  - weight: 74.5 kg
Provider -> Provider: Sort entries by date
Provider -> Profile: Update userProfile.weight = 74.5
Provider -> Provider: Save to SharedPreferences:\n- weightEntries array\n- userProfile
Provider -> Provider: notifyListeners()
Provider --> Dialog: Weight logged
deactivate Provider

alt Sync to Cloud
    Dialog -> Supabase: logWeight(74.5, today)
    activate Supabase
    Supabase --> Dialog: Synced to cloud
    deactivate Supabase
end

Dialog --> User: Show success message
Dialog -> Progress: Close dialog
deactivate Dialog

== Update Chart ==

Progress -> Provider: Listen to changes
activate Provider
Provider --> Progress: Updated weightEntries
deactivate Provider

Progress -> Chart: Re-render chart
activate Chart

Chart -> Chart: Recalculate statistics:\n- Weight change: -0.5 kg this week\n- Total change: -5 kg (from start)\n- Trend: Losing\n- BMI: 23.3 (Normal)

Chart --> User: Animate chart update:\n- New data point added\n- Trend line updated\n- Stats refreshed

alt Weight Goal Reached
    Chart --> User: Show celebration:\n"🎉 Goal weight reached!"
end

deactivate Chart

== View Weight History ==

User -> Progress: Scroll weight chart
activate Progress

Progress --> User: Display all weight entries:\n- May 20: 74.5 kg\n- May 13: 75.0 kg\n- May 6: 76.0 kg\n- Apr 29: 77.5 kg\n- Apr 22: 78.0 kg

User -> Progress: Long press on entry
Progress --> User: Show entry details:\n- Date\n- Weight\n- Change from previous\n- Days since entry

deactivate Progress

== Toggle Weight Unit ==

User -> Progress: Click unit toggle (kg ↔ lbs)
activate Progress

Progress -> Provider: Update weight unit
activate Provider

Provider -> Provider: userProfile.weightUnit = "lbs"
Provider -> Provider: Convert all weights:\n  75 kg → 165.3 lbs
Provider -> Provider: Save to SharedPreferences
Provider -> Provider: notifyListeners()
Provider --> Progress: Unit updated
deactivate Provider

Progress -> Chart: Re-render with new unit
activate Chart
Chart --> User: Display chart in lbs:\n- Current: 165.3 lbs\n- Change: -1.1 lbs\n- BMI: 23.3 (unchanged)
deactivate Chart

deactivate Progress

== Weight Insights ==

Progress -> Chart: Calculate insights
activate Chart

Chart -> Chart: Analyze data:\n- Check if on track for goal\n- Calculate rate of change\n- Compare to healthy range\n- Generate recommendations

Chart --> User: Show insights:\n"📊 You're losing 0.5 kg/week\n✅ Healthy rate (goal: lose 0.5 kg/week)\n💪 Keep up the good work!\n🎯 10 weeks to goal weight"

deactivate Chart

== BMI Calculation ==

note right of Provider
  **BMI Formula:**
  BMI = weight (kg) / (height (m))²

  **Example:**
  Weight: 74.5 kg
  Height: 175 cm = 1.75 m

  BMI = 74.5 / (1.75 × 1.75)
      = 74.5 / 3.0625
      = 24.3

  **Categories:**
  < 18.5: Underweight
  18.5-24.9: Normal
  25-29.9: Overweight
  ≥ 30: Obese

  **Weekly Change Calculation:**
  (Current - Previous) / Days * 7
  = (74.5 - 75.0) / 7 * 7
  = -0.5 kg/week
end note

== Sync Weight History ==

Supabase -> Provider: Real-time subscription\n(profile changes)
activate Supabase
activate Provider

Supabase --> Provider: Weight updated remotely
Provider -> Provider: Fetch latest weight history
Provider -> Provider: Merge with local data
Provider -> Provider: notifyListeners()
Provider --> Progress: Data synchronized
deactivate Provider
deactivate Supabase

Progress --> User: Update displayed chart\n(seamless background sync)

@enduml

